Jmeter
Step 1: How we  Install and run Jmeter
1. Prerequest : Java (check java in your system   java -version)
2. Download Jmeter Binaries  http://jmeter.apache.org/download_jmeter.cgi
3. unzip meter at any location
4. start jmeter
    1. Windows  : meter/bin -> jmeter.bat
    2. Mac : openterminal -> jmeter/bin -> sh jmeter.sh
    
    
